snippet.textDisplay:
This song is pure magic ✨ The line ‘Jab tak neende na aaye inn Lakeero mein baatein ho’ just stays with me, it feels like a whole story wrapped in one line. ❤️ 
Anup's voice, the emotions, the simplicity, everything about this performance is perfect. I admire how humble he looks and I wish he is, it makes the song feel even more personal and real. 

Thank you for creating something that touches the heart every single time I listen to it. 🎶❤
